        <ul>
          <li>Quarantining sick people never works because that just makes a horde of zombies.</li>
          <li>Figure out medical tests to catch the infection early.</li>
          <li>Provided the disease isn't airborne, move government and key facilities to islands so resources can be protected.</li>
          <li>If the outbreak is small, keep infected sedated and locked away while looking for a cute. Otherwise, don't hesitate to shoot at the head. Sacrifices must be made to ensure our survival!</li>
        </ul>
