        <ul>
          <li>Get to an area of low population density.</li>
          <li>Find a defensible location, both from zombies and from looters.</li>
          <li>Your greatest threat deep in the game will be other looters, so you have to screen every survivor you come across.</li>
          <li>Keep your whereabouts low-key while gathering more resources (food, fuel, etc). Use heat, solar, or human power instead of generators where you can.</li>
